2. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper proposes a scheme for image security, which falls under the domain of cryptography and security. 
3. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper involves optimization of multiple cascaded phase masks, which can be viewed as an information theory problem. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with image encryption and watermarking, which are common topics in multimedia. 
5. cs.OH (Optimization and Control) - The paper involves optimization of multiple cascaded phase masks, which can be viewed as an optimization and control problem.
